===Noun===
'''[[reflux]] [[condenser]]'''
#{{chemistry}} a [[water-cooled]], [[double walled]] piece of [[laboratory]] [[glassware]] that is fitted on top of a [[vessel]] of [[boiling]] [[liquid]] such that [[vapour]] [[condense]]s and flows back into the vessel, preventing the contents from boiling dry
